title: AC-DC Live (resequenced & expanded by }{eywood)
description:
AC/DC Live
resequenced and expanded by }{eywood

All I've really done here is to shuffle the order of the songs a little bit, add the single B-side to the running order and omit the fadeouts between songs so the thing sounds like a single show.
